item.title: Dreams are cool, but reality is better!
item.description: Here’s a glimpse into what the first version of New York Villa looks like: Beautiful right? You’ll be captivated by this quality, low maintenance 225 square contemporary estate. Set in a quiet family-oriented community, there’s ease of access to local shops, sport centers, the freeway and it’s just 2 minutes drive from to Shelta New York Villa I. This striking estate offers contemporary Nigerian family living at its best.
